          ></a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/avtoelon.uz/"
            ><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram fa-xl"></i
          ></a>
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Avtoelon.uz/"
            ><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f fa-xl"></i
          ></a>
          <a href="https://youtube.com/@choynakningqopqogi?si=quiKZaNcuWjFH6By"
